{
  "texts": [
    "For example, the formal name of an entity was used (\"Lesch-Nyhan syndrome\") if a variant was missed (\"lesch nyhan\").",
    "If the formal name was the missed term, a broader term that would encompass the formal name (\"purine salvage deficiencies\") was used as the target entity.",
    "We report the proportion of entities missed during NER that were recovered through this augmentation step.",
    "The selected entities are used to develop a regular expression tool for information retrieval.",
    "Specifically, we employed the Target Matcher provided by MedSpaCy 72."
  ]
}